<h2>Costume Story</h2><p class="para-1">
Assassin: I am not used to such thin clothing.<br>
<br>
<i> As the woman dons her disguise, she attempts to wrap a pareo
around her waist. As she does, a hidden weapon clatters to the floor.</i><br>
<br>
 Assassin: I really need more places to hide things.<br><br>
<i> She takes her hat in hand and pauses briefly in contemplation.</i><br><br>

 Assassin: I wonder why they use both an umbrella and a hat?</p>
